step_data.thought: I've successfully reached the Braintree Virtual Terminal page as indicated by the page title 'Braintree Virtual Terminal / Operations / Sales / Magento Admin'. However, I notice there's a dialog box with an 'Attention' message stating 'Please configure your Braintree Payments account in order to use the virtual terminal.' This indicates that before I can use the virtual terminal for payment processing, the Braintree Payments account needs to be configured first. I should acknowledge this message by clicking the 'OK' button with ID [775] to proceed.
